        "timestamp": "2018-02-23 01:10:16.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nI checked only those three pom files has logback.\n\n./appc-sdc-listener/appc-sdc-listener-bundle/pom.xml:115:\t\t\t<artifactId>logback-core</artifactId>\n./pom.xml:347:                <artifactId>logback-core</artifactId>\n./appc-common/pom.xml:45:      <artifactId>logback-core</artifactId>\n./appc-sdc-listener/appc-sdc-listener-bundle/pom.xml:119:\t\t\t<artifactId>logback-classic</artifactId>\n./pom.xml:353:                <artifactId>logback-classic</artifactId>\n./appc-common/pom.xml:51:      <artifactId>logback-classic</artifactId>\n\n\nbut only the top of pom.xml specifies the version number. but maybe my eye was not good...\n\nalso ran mvn dependency:tree all shows the new version...",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
